ough getting vaccinated. <img class="wp-image-533044 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/02/Portia-Zambuko.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/02/Portia-Zambuko.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/02/Portia-Zambuko-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Sister Portia Zambuko checks BP count for Mr Mzingaye Mphoko who is a health worker under the private sector at Health Kings pharmacy in Gwanda before he gets vacinnated (Picture by Austin Nyathi) More details to follow @mthabisi_mthire